# Documentation & Comments Rules

- **Rule 5.1 (Purposeful Comments):** Comment the *why* for non-obvious code, not the *what*.
- **Rule 5.2 (API Documentation):** Document public APIs (functions, classes, methods) using standard conventions (e.g., JSDoc, Docstrings).
